listData.name: 180 Day Business Term Deposit
listData.description: A fixed term investment for businesses at an agreed rate of interest.

features.additionalValue: Includes access to digital banking services
features.additionalInfo: The Tyro App lets you access 24/7 mobile banking so you can stay on top of your business from anywhere.
We'll notify you via email a week before your term deposit matures as well as the day before so you don't forget.
If you want to withdraw your Term Deposit before it matures you'll need to give us 31 days' notice. Your interest payment may be reduced.

eligibility.additionalInfo: You must be a Tyro EFTPOS/eCommerce with an active Tyro Bank Account to open a Tyro Business Term Deposit.
You must have an active ABN.
